          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "    25.4 X 25.4  CM    NAI   detector  with  an",
                " anticoincidence shield  was  used  for  the (p,g) and",
                " (a,g) reactions gamma-quanta registration."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DTBAL"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "   The  (g,p-0)  and  (g,a-0)  reactions  cross",
                " sections were  obtained from the data for (p,g-0) and",
                " (a,g-0) reactions using  the  principle  of  detailed",
                " balance."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Statistical errors are given."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A comparison  is  made between the yield curves of the",
                " measured Cr-52(a,g-0) and Mn-55(p,g-0)  reactions  in",
                " the giant  dipole  resonance region of Fe-56 (E-exc =",
                " 14.0 to  21.5  MeV)  to  determine   if   the   gross",
                " differences can   be  interpreted  as  being  due  to",
                " isospin effects.  Above 18 MeV the yield of  (g,a-0),",
                " determined by  the principle of detailed balance,  is",
                " observed to drop below the value  obtained  when  the",
                " energy dependence of the transmission coefficients is",
                " removed. This leads to the conclusion that while  the",
                " diminished yield in the (g,a-0) channel may be due to",
                " the failure to  populate  the  isospin  forbidden  T>",
                " states, other effects cannot be ruled out."
              ]
            }
          ],
